spirent.methodology.RunSqlCommand.DbJsonString: { "sql_operations": [{ "db_information": { "db_name": "SUMMARY" }, "sql_statement": [{ "static": "CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations ('FrameSize' INTEGER, 'Load' FLOAT, 'ILoad' FLOAT, 'OLoad' FLOAT, 'TheoreticalFrameRate' INTERGER, 'FrameForwardingRate' INTEGER, 'FrameLoss' INTEGER, 'TotalFrameCount' INTEGER, 'TxPort' VARCHAR, 'RxPort' VARCHAR)" }] }, { "db_information": { "db_name": "LAST_ITERATION" }, "sql_statement": [{ "static": "SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'FrameSize', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Load', ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0 / 8) / Sb.PercentageLoad) As 'ILoad', Sb.MbpsLoad AS 'OLoad', ROUND((Sb.FpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad) AS 'TheoreticalFrameRate', ROUND((RxRes.FrameCount)/((LastArrivalTime - FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) AS 'FrameForwardingRate', DroppedFrameCount AS 'FrameLoss', SigFrameCount + DroppedFrameCount - DuplicateFrameCount AS 'TotalFrameCount', TxRes.PortName AS 'TxPort', RxRes.PortName AS 'RxPort' FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle" }], "temp_table_name": "MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations" }] }
